        <title>The name module </title>
        <annotation annotates="/">
            <para>This module defines the name element for identifying proper names. </para>
            <para>More information about this module is available at http://www.daisy.org/z3986/2011/auth/cm/#z3986.name.module</para>
        </annotation>
